        "richtext_bcLkkx": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Situated on 20 privately owned acres, Sweet Honey Farm is reimagining the tradition of private communities. Moving beyond the former model of strict rules, dress codes and divisions by gender - we're offering a new approach in which a unique blend of wellness, productivity, and diverse community are at the forefront.</p>",
            "text_size": 16,
            "text_bottom_spacing": 20
          }
        },
        "richtext_dtDLmq": {
          "type": "richtext",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Our CSA Membership is not just about access to amazing amenities — it's about the people you will share these spaces with. In order to maintain integrity and cultivate a community of like-minded individuals who support and inspire each other.</p>",
            "text_size": 16,
            "text_bottom_spacing": 20
          }
        }
      },
