            "image": "shopify://shop_images/shf.jpg",
            "subheading": "",
            "heading": "Our Three Pillars",
            "text": "<p>Find yourself immersed in a world of unique, engaged community across three major pillars designed to enrich your daily routine and provide a peaceful escape from the busyness of everyday life:</p><h5>Farm Experiences</h5><p>Immerse yourself in farm life and experience the physical and mental health benefits that come with getting hands-on. Pick fresh produce in the garden, connect with animals, collect fresh eggs and more.<br/></p><h5>World-Class Amenities</h5><p>Exclusive amenities centered around wellness and recovery. Members enjoy unlimited access to everything from saunas, red-light therapy, cold plunges, infrared sauna and more.</p><p></p><h5>Community Events</h5><p>Be part of our vibrant community through purposeful events like farm Fridays, family days, movie nights, farm education classes, and weekly group workouts.</p>",
